Template: igestis_samba/install_ldap
Type: boolean
_Description: Do you want that iGestis automatically installs OpenLDAP:
 In order to use this module, you have to install Samba schema.
 This step is a little bit hard to do by hand, so iGestis-samba is
 able to do this for you.
 .
 iGestis will add Samba schema and necessary Organisation Unit.